Introduction

Eunice, formerly known as Sooyeon, is a South Korean singer associated with RXM and 12ENT. She is a member of the girl group DIA and its sub-unit BCHCS. Eunice made her debut with DIA on September 14, 2015, with the release of their first studio album, "Do It Amazing." On December 29, 2016, she became part of DIA's first sub-unit, BCHCS.
